Enum Class TileEdge

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<TileEdge>
it.polimi.it.galaxytrucker.model.componenttiles.TileEdge
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<TileEdge>, Constable
public enum TileEdge extends Enum<TileEdge>
Represents the possible edge types of a tile in the game, defining their compatibility rules. Each edge type implements isCompatible to determine if it can connect with another edge.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Giacomo Amaducci

  • Enum Constant Summary

    Enum Constants
    Enum Constant
    Description
    DOUBLE
    An edge with a double connector on it.
    INCOMPATIBLE
    Represents an incompatible edge type used for cannon fronts and engine backs, which require an empty cell.
    SINGLE
    An edge with a single connector on it.
    SMOOTH
    An edge with no connectors on it.
    UNIVERSAL
    An edge with a universal connector that can connect with any other connector type.
